nodes.text: The Wookiee underground resistance movement, also known simply as the Wookiee resistance, was an organization of Wookiees based on Kashyyyk that was active by 2 BBY. Led by Katarra, they actively opposed the presence on their planet of the Galactic Empire, who had turned Kashyyyk into a slave world. Jowdrrl and Ralera were also members. During the Galactic Civil War, the resistance movement was led by the Wookiee warrior Ulaaar.
